  "title": "Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p>KICK START your Marketing journey with us!</p><p>We are seeking a potential Marketing Executive to join our digital marketing team.</p><p>Your primary responsibility will be to contact potential customers and engage them to show up at outlets.<br /></p><ul><li>Respond to customer enquiries via all communication channels timely, including whatsapp, call pm, email, etc.</li><li>Design effective and persuasive talking points and messages to improve conversion rate.</li><li>Booking appointments in system.</li><li>Maintain customer information in CRM system, e.g. hubspot</li><li>Brief campaign mechanics with sales and operation team.</li><li>Track daily trial sales and provide performance report by weekly, monthly, quarterly.</li><li>Enhance chatbot automation process.</li><li>Assist in other tasks assigned by manager.</li><li>Patient and good interpersonal communication skills.</li><li>At least a Diploma in Marketing, Communications, or a related field is preferred.</li><li>Good at office software, e.g. excel, PPT.</li><li>Must be proficient in both English and Mandarin due to marketing contents.</li><li>Prior experience in beauty and wellness industry is a bonus.</li><li>Willingness to learn.</li><li></li></ul><p>Full time</p><p>Monday to Friday Office Hours.</p><p>Location: Jalan Bukit Merah</p>",
